<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Maximum width in pixels</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter the maximum width in pixels for images of this size. If your item image exceeds this size, then the displayed image will be scaled down. The aspect ratio will stay the same.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Max. lifetime of cache in days</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter the number of days that created images are saved in the CloudFront cache. The image’s lifetime begins once the image has been displayed on screen in this size, i.e. loaded into the cache.</p></td>
