<p>Select if original images are to be enlarged.</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Not activated</strong> = Images are scaled to size if the original image is smaller than the maximum dimensions defined for this size.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div></div></td>
