<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter a compression for original JPG images in percent. Compression reduces load times and can help you achieve better page speed values.<br>
<strong><em>Tip:</em></strong> Compressing images to 80&nbsp;% results in no visible loss of quality.</p></td>
</tr>
